n of Mr. Smith. 他們總是嘲弄史密斯先生。<br />\n<br />\n    2. 永遠，一直<br />\n<br />\n    Labor Day is always the first Monday of September. 勞工節一直是九月的第一個禮拜一。<br />\n<br />\n    3. （動詞用進行式）老是，一再<br />\n<br />\n    I'm always misplacing my glasses. 我老是將眼鏡亂放而找不到。<br />\n<br />\n    4. （與can/could連用）隨時<br />\n<br />\n    You can always resign if you feel unhappy. 如果你不滿意，隨時可以辭職。"},{"pid":"ac11bbc5736dfc665a9fc1836a96455aa4b30e18","tid":621590,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6beae5a6afc74fbc2d0b89cb6f1185c574b2f694","tid":621590,"uid":179810,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T15:21:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://wiki.komica.org/images/f/f5/Img12505.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwiki.komica.org%2Fimages%2Ff%2Ff5%2FImg12505.jpg&h=caab4110&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:08:31.000Z","msg":"一直想搵番呢幅圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b22c1f6fd35061d2cd0af83741c4ee18b177462","tid":621590,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12e0bb730ce50c13e81d18be1f7c3a1602c40210","tid":621590,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7dceed87c8ed646823732deda1971ce68b7db73","tid":621590,"uid":6347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T15:05:00.000Z","msg":"Always唔係解永遠呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-08T16:07:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://tw.dictionary.search.yahoo.com/search?p=always\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftw.dictionary.search.yahoo.com%2Fsearch%3Fp%3Dalways&d=gCaSkHP6TFZNESPGO7qoUS7PofNJLCAwyGXsi6MH%2FEQ%3D&h=f30ad063\" target=\"_blank\">http://tw.dictionary.search.yahoo.com/search?p=always</a><br />\n<br />\nalways<br />\n<br />\n    KK[ˋɔlwez] DJ[ˋɔ:lweiz] <br />\n<br />\n美式<br />\n<br />\n    adv.<br />\n    總是，經常；永遠，一直<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n    adv.<br />\n    副